<L>__{interior salvadoran diner booth day}
<A>__{ginger is in a booth with lester diamond, handing him the envelope filled with money.}
<C>__{lester}
<D>__{what does that mean? no, i know that look. what does that mean?}
<C>__{ginger}
<D>__{it means i got the money.}
