<C>__{ace}
<D>__{if i'm wrong, please correct me, 'cause i never knew you to be a heist man.}
<P>__{(lester sighs.)}
<D>__{but if you are, you know what... here, take mine too.}
<A>__{ace takes some money out of his coat and puts the thick wad of bills on the table.}
<C>__{ace}
<D>__{go ahead, take it. 'cause you already have hers.}
<A>__{lester turns and sees two hoods standing by the front and back doors of the diner.}
<C>__{ace}
<D>__{she's my wife.}
