<D>__{you do? yeah? well, if you ever come back again... ever... to take her money... next time bring a pistol. that way you got a chance. be a man, don't be a fuckin' pimp. now, you want to do me a favor? get out of here. i want to be alone with my wife. get the fuck up and get out of here.}
